{
  "stem": "19502.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 343.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You wouldn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], you know, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we were going then, that time, with [INAUDIBLE], with our own generators and so on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I went with [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She's now in Israel, so the two of us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were good students, so we-- we didn't have to pay, we got [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the-- the weekends we had to work on the [NON-ENGLISH] because it was so badly bombed.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we worked with the prisoner of wars, together.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they were under the guard and we were-- we were cleaning up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So now-- now when I was in Kiev, I says, I worked in there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then the school, they used to send us-- weekends, we had to take their-- their-- their uniforms, go the Dnieper, and wash it in cold water.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They gave us a bunch of uniforms.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And bring it back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was our days off.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And summer, we had to go and work on the [NON-ENGLISH], because you know, for our-- that time, I just thought that we were-- they did us any harm, it's not right.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But when I see it now, I mean, they-- listen, we had to pay somehow for our teaching.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that was, I think, a six months course, whatever.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then they kept sending us from place to place to project.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, most of them were the movies from the war, most of them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We showed one which is a-- a classic for-- with [NON-ENGLISH], the-- the-- the-- the movie star.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Paul Muni, you know, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Black and white.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And every time it used to tear in the middle, so they used to scream at us and so on.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That how I met Leo's father.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was working.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was projecting moves in the-- their town.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
